### Churches

The [Cremona Cathedral](/Cremona_Cathedral), standing adjacent to the [Baptistery](/Battistero_di_Cremona), presents one of northern Italy's most significant collections of Romanesque-Gothic art. It’s a place that demands your attention, not just for its age, but for the sheer artistry and history it embodies.

Beyond the cathedral complex, Cremona boasts a number of other notable churches:

*   [Sant'Agata](/Sant%27Agata,_Cremona)
*   [Sant'Agostino](/Sant%27Agostino,_Cremona)
*   [San Facio](/San_Facio,_Cremona)
